high_descs: Pick up the large pot on the right from the stove.
Bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Bring the pot to the stove.
Put the pot on the stove in the back right.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove to your right.
Take the pot on the bottom right corner of the stove.
Turn around and go left to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Turn around and go right to return to the fridge.
Place the pot on the back right corner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight, and then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn around, take a few steps, and then turn left towards the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge for it to cool and then take it out of the fridge.
Turn around, head towards the toaster, and then turn right towards the stove.
Place the pot to the right of the other pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Cool down one of the pots on the stove.
